==Mandarin==
===Idiom===
{{PAGENAME}} (''[[Pinyin]]'' bùguăn sān qī èr shí yī)
# casting all caution to the winds; come what may; in spite of anything; recklessly; regardless of anything; regardless of the consequences; whatever may happen.

